<p>world is coming to an end today. Heavy artillery fire. We expect to storm the Pozieres wood tonight. The wood is on our left front. Our H.Q. is in a German dugout about 30 feet underground. The enemy brought down one of our planes about 50 yards from our line 20.7.16</p>
